indicator_descEN: Annual growth rate of real GDP per employed person
seriesDescription: Annual growth rate of real GDP per employed person (%)
footnotes: Based on GDP per person engaged, constant 2010 US dollar
sources: ILO modelled estimates, November 2019, available in ILOSTAT (https://ilostat.ilo.org/). For the specific sources by country and the estimation methodology refer to ILOSTAT directly.
